<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: comic sans ms,sans-serif; font-size: small;">- make new friends</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: comic sans ms,sans-serif; font-size: small;">- share stories and information</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: comic sans ms,sans-serif; font-size: small;">- ask others for opinions and insights</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: comic sans ms,sans-serif; font-size: small;">- mentor and coach others</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: comic sans ms,sans-serif; font-size: small;">all while doing what they like best, playing a game and competing to win.&nbsp; </span></p>
</p>', '2010-12-02 00:00:00', 'Mission', '2010-12-02 15:30:50', 'New Mission', 2, 3, null, 'Our Mission', 'ACTIVE');
